{"tid":2218310,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"一人n句返工嘅時候客人對自己講啲奇怪説話","createTime":"2020-09-26T06:20:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T07:48:41.000Z","uid":181997,"like":13,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5da71f0ee1eda53766a81ccddf6b35114ff8f7d5","tid":2218310,"uid":181997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:20:04.000Z","msg":"有個好可愛嘅小妹妹行埋嚟，好細聲怕怕醜醜咁喺我耳邊講<br />\n&rdquo;哥哥，可摸耳幫我整大啲個音道？&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有日返工要追數所以親自電腦送外賣<br />\n點知上到個客屋企，係個吊帶絲質睡裙少婦開門，咁我咪放底部腦俾佢簽收，之後我就閃人囉，<br />\n點知個少婦捉住我個衫袖，問我<br />\n&ldquo;你走嗱！你唔係會同我砌埋先走㗎，咁我典線？&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"668952177414bf140d043af5fbe0e2111a5adecf","tid":2218310,"uid":70454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:23:20.000Z","msg":"唔好笑囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9537ddb15426f3177ff79c2f1c8714f126fe1bac","tid":2218310,"uid":181997,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"668952177414bf140d043af5fbe0e2111a5adecf","tid":2218310,"uid":70454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:23:20.000Z","msg":"唔好笑囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:24:00.000Z","msg":"真人真事，咪當我講笑話先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28577f164facd07ef580cbb340a52d8ac1922981","tid":2218310,"uid":126226,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T06:25:59.000Z","msg":"屌 有棍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38763a2880a1602d851546778b7899ba301d871f","tid":2218310,"uid":181997,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28577f164facd07ef580cbb340a52d8ac1922981","tid":2218310,"uid":126226,"like":3,"d